window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Siobhan Spencer is a former child movie star, but her past still comes back to haunt her. After a long string of dates who judged her because they knew who she was, Siobhan decided to take a break from dating. That is, until her roommate sets her up with Jacob, who has never heard of Siobhan. <br> <br> But her past has a way of ruining what could be a great relationship. Siobhan must face her insecurities, if she hopes to make things right again. If she doesn’t, she’ll lose Jacob forever.</p>"; 
